Uses of Package
com.saurabh.entity

  • Packages that use com.saurabh.entity 
    Package Description
    com.saurabh.controller
    Provides necessary classes for implementing the REST APIs for all the four Entities which are : Student, Course, Teacher, and Fee
    com.saurabh.dao
    Provides necessary classes for implementing the CRUD operations on all the four Entities which are : Student, Course, Teacher, and Fee
    com.saurabh.entity
    Provides necessary POJO Entity Classes and establishes a meaningful relationship between those entity classes.
    com.saurabh.service
    Provides necessary Service Layers for each Entity which mediates the communication between the REST Controller and the Repository.
  • Classes in com.saurabh.entity used by com.saurabh.controller 
    Class and Description
    Course
    This Class is a Course Entity which has all the variables related to course details and has a one-to-many relationship with Teacher Entity and one-to-one relationship with Fee Entity
    Fee
    This Class is a Fee Entity which has all the variables related to fee details and has a one-to-one relationship with Course Entity
    Student
    This Class is a Student Entity which has all the variables related to student details and has a one-to-one relationship with Course Entity
    Teacher
    This Class is a Teacher Entity which has all the variables related to teacher details and has a many-to-one relationship with Course Entity
